  "Description": {
    "English": "A living, fertile egg, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">ready to hatch!</span><br><br>The beast within wriggles and fidgets, yearning to unfurl its long neck.<br><br>Scans indicate the being within has the genetic potential for a <span class=\"name name-stellar\">loyal</span> nature, longing to find a master to place at the center of its universe.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一枚有生命的、可孵化的卵，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">已经准备好孵化！</span><br><br>卵壳内的生物躁动着不断扭动，迫不及待要伸展它修长的脖颈。<br><br>根据扫描结果显示，里面的生物拥有<span class=\"name name-stellar\">忠诚</span>的基因潜质，渴望找到主人并将其视为宇宙的中心。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "有生命、可孵化的蛋，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">且即將孵化！</span><br><br>裡面的野獸不安地蠕動著，渴望伸展牠長長的脖子。<br><br>掃描結果顯示，該生物可能擁有以下形容的大小及特徵：<span class=\"name name-stellar\">忠心</span>性情，想要找到主人，並將對方視為宇宙的中心。"
  },
